TI  - Elevation determines the productivity of large cardamom (Amomum subulatum Roxb.) cultivars in Sikkim Himalaya
T2  - SCIENTIFIC REPORTS
LA  - English
KW  - CLIMATE-CHANGE
KW  - RANGE SHIFTS
