TI  - The acacia plantation boom in Thu'a Thien Hue Province, Central Vietnam: A survey of tree farmers' shifting livelihoods, environmental perceptions, and occupational perspectives
T2  - TREES FORESTS AND PEOPLE
LA  - English
KW  - Agricultural transition
KW  - Forestland tenure
