TI  - The Spatio-Temporal Analysis of Droughts Using the Standardized Precipitation Evapotranspiration Index and Its Impact on Cereal Yields in a Semi-Arid Mediterranean Region
T2  - APPLIED SCIENCES-BASEL
LA  - English
KW  - drought
