TI  - When hazards become disasters: coastal fishing communities in Bangladesh
T2  - ENVIRONMENTAL HAZARDS-HUMAN AND POLICY DIMENSIONS
LA  - English
KW  - Disaster
KW  - hazard
KW  - DPSIR framework
KW  - Bangladesh
