TI  - Comparative profitability and relative risk of adopting climate-smart soil practices among farmers. A cost-benefit analysis of six agricultural practices
T2  - CLIMATE SERVICES
LA  - English
KW  - Climate-smart soils
KW  - Deterministic cost-benefit analysis
KW  - Profitability
