TI  - Farmers' perceptions and management of risk in rice/shrimp farming systems in South-West Coastal Bangladesh
T2  - LAND USE POLICY
LA  - English
KW  - Production risk
KW  - Market risk
KW  - Risk management
KW  - Rice
KW  - Shrimp
KW  - Farming systems
