TI  - United Kingdom's fruit and vegetable supply is increasingly dependent on imports from climate-vulnerable producing countries
T2  - NATURE FOOD
LA  - English
KW  - FRESH VEGETABLES
KW  - AGRICULTURE
KW  - GOVERNANCE
KW  - IMPACTS
KW  - AFRICA
