TI  - Time to re-think the GMO revolution in agriculture
T2  - ECOLOGICAL INFORMATICS
LA  - English
KW  - Seed production
KW  - Crop commodities
KW  - Transgenic soybean varieties
KW  - Transgenic hybrid maize
