TI  - Physiological, metabolomic, morphological and root system architecture acclimation responses to drought in the African orphan millet white fonio (Digitaria exilis)
T2  - PLANT AND SOIL
LA  - English
KW  - Fonio
KW  - Millet
KW  - Drought
KW  - Root system architecture
KW  - Physiology
KW  - Sahel
KW  - WATER-STRESS
