TI  - Social-ecological interactions in the Draa River Basin, southern Morocco: Towards nature conservation and human well-being using the IPBES framework
T2  - SCIENCE OF THE TOTAL ENVIRONMENT
LA  - English
KW  - DNA barcoding
KW  - Desert rivers
KW  - Ecosystem services
KW  - Transdisciplinarity
