TI  - Jatropha cultivation in southern India: assessing farmers' experiences
T2  - BIOFUELS BIOPRODUCTS & BIOREFINING-BIOFPR
LA  - English
KW  - interviews
KW  - perceptions
KW  - drivers and barriers
KW  - biofuel policies and implementation
