TI  - Challenging slopes: ethnic minority livelihoods, state visions, and land-use land cover change in Vietnam's northern mountainous borderlands
T2  - ENVIRONMENT DEVELOPMENT AND SUSTAINABILITY
LA  - English
KW  - Livelihoods
