TI  - An assessment of agroforestry as a climate-smart practice: Evidences from farmers of northwestern region of Bangladesh
T2  - AGROSYSTEMS GEOSCIENCES & ENVIRONMENT
LA  - English
KW  - FOOD SECURITY
KW  - AGRICULTURE
