TI  - Food security and vulnerability of farmers household in the South of Bakhtegan Lake, Iran: uncovering patterns through data mining perspective
T2  - ENVIRONMENT DEVELOPMENT AND SUSTAINABILITY
LA  - English
KW  - Data mining
