TI  - Participatory variety selection and characterization of Sorghum (Sorghum bicolor (L.) Moench) elite accessions from Malawian gene pool using farmer and breeder knowledge
T2  - AFRICAN JOURNAL OF AGRICULTURAL RESEARCH
LA  - English
