TI  - Role of Agroforestry on Farmland Productivity in Semi-arid Farming Regions of Zimbabwe
T2  - RESEARCH ON WORLD AGRICULTURAL ECONOMY
LA  - English
KW  - Adoption
KW  - Crop productivity
KW  - Drought
