TI  - Efficacy of risk reducing diversification portfolio strategies among agro-pastoralists in semi-arid area: A modern portfolio theory approach
T2  - JOURNAL OF AGRICULTURE AND FOOD RESEARCH
LA  - English
KW  - Modern portfolio theory
