TI  - A global assessment of the vulnerability of shellfish aquaculture to climate change and ocean acidification
T2  - ECOLOGY AND EVOLUTION
LA  - English
KW  - aquaculture
KW  - climate change
KW  - food-security
KW  - ocean acidification
KW  - shellfish
